						Online bidding takes down the barriers to accessing your auctions. Potential bidders don't have to wait to place bids,
						they can do so at any time and from almost anywhere.<br />
						<br />
						And when bidders are outbid they are notified and prompted to increase their absentee amount on the spot,
						reducing disappointed bidders and increasing hammer prices.
					</span>
				</p>
				
