						Those bids will push prices up, you'll sell more items and at higher prices.<br />
						<br />
						Not only will people in your auction area have easier access and less barriers to accessing your auctions,
						but a whole world of bidders will now have the ability to access your auctions from wherever they might be!
					</span>
				</p>
				
