						<br />
						Now the busiest person can still take a moment to sign-on and bid without disturbing their schedule.<br />
						Even loyal bidders go out of town, with live online bidding they can be in a different country and still make it to your live auction via their laptop!
						There is no need for bidders to be deprived of the interactive live auction experience.<br />
